-- Canadian Tire to sell 20 pct stake in financial services business
-- By Ashutosh Pandey in Bangalore
-- Thu May 08, 2014 07:50AM EDT
-- None



May 8 (Reuters) - Canadian Tire Corp <CTCa.TO> said Bank of Nova Scotia <BNS.TO> <BNS.N> would buy a 20 percent stake in the retailer's financial services business for C$500 million ($459 million) in cash.

The bank will have the option to buy an additional 29 percent of the business within 10 years. [ID:nMKWN02gHa]